
This is Frama-C XX.X

Usage:
    frama-c [options files ...]

Main Options:
    -help        This message.
    -version     Version number only.
    -plugins     List of installed plugins.
    -kernel-h    Additional help and options.

Plug-in Options:
    -<plugin>    Plug-in activation.
    -<plugin>-h  Additional help and options.

